Helen Westcott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Westcott 0 Helen Westcott (born Myrthas Helen Hickman, January 1, 1928 – March 17, 1998) was an American stage and screen actor and former child actor. She is best known for her work in The Gunfighter (1950).
